text: Warren Mellie (born October 1, 1994) is a Seychellois football player. He is a defender playing for the Seychelles national football team and has represented Seychelles in the AFCON 2018. He also plays for the Northern Dynamo FC. == References == Category:Living people Category:1994 births Category:Seychellois footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Seychelles international footballers
